plot: Angry, pervy, outrageous and hilarious Fleabag arrives with a bang, as she spins through the city grasping at anyone and anything that might keep her head above water.

Speaking direct to camera, girl about town Fleabag recounts her day starting with a one night stand and a bus pickup to whom she explains how she recently split from boyfriend Harry. After being refused a bank loan for her struggling café she meets - and argues yet again - with sister Claire at a feminist lecture before visiting estranged Dad and Godmother - whom he married with indecent haste on widowhood - helping a drunk woman and pleasuring herself in a taxi.—don @ minifie-1
